    "text": {
      "_dirName": "text",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "  My mysterious Specter,\\r \\rYou're everything I've ever wanted: Tall, dark, and handsome. I can't keep your haunting voice off my mind. I even wake up with chills just thinking about you! Isn't it spooky how good we are together?"
    }
